author: dws
msg: expat.patch: Track changes in build.conf.  Take out all xmlparse.h and
add include for expat.h.
install.patch: Ignore temporary file (ends with T) and just copy normal
module file.
subversion.spec: Took out dependency on libxml by building neon package
correctly.  This also applied to w3c-libwww package.  Also the
subversion-server package now only takes stuff out of the httpd.conf
file when it is being erased, not upgraded.

author: gstein
msg: Hook up Karl's log report into mod_dav_svn
* version.c (avail_reports[]): add new "svn:log-report" to the list
(dav_svn_get_report): restructure for easier addition of
reports. add the new log-report option, to call dav_svn__log_report
* log.c (log_receiver): fix the header of the report -- output namespaces
and use the correct name for the report. deliver properly
structured XML items in the report.
(dav_svn__log_report): correct the check for child namespace -- it
needs to apply to all the elements. some stylistic nits.

author: gstein
msg: Fix checkouts of things other than the root.
(begin_checkout): stop using svn_path_add_component_nts(). it doesn't
work properly (it doesn't handle separators correctly). go back to
our old broken way of creating the bc_root until path.c is fixed.
